      </p>
      <img
        src="/imagenes/multicenter.png"
        alt="Multicenter"
        class="w-36 h-auto object-contain mb-5"
      />
      <a
        href="https://wa.link/tmre7t"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="boton-accion"
      >
